  "texts": [
    "Drug response data were retrieved from the GDSC and CTRP databases [24] [25] [26] [27], covering a total of 692,859 cell line-drug pairs comprising 1,244 cell lines and 888 drugs.",
    "The data from the two datasets were harmonized as follows.",
    "Drug information: each molecule's published name, synonym or SMILES (Simplified Molecular Input Line Entry System) string was queried using PubChemPy.",
    "The associated InChIKey was extracted and used to identify duplicate drugs (within or between datasets).",
    "Cell viability data: for CTRP, the vehicle control-normalized average percent viability files were used."
  ],
